  "text": "This work stems from failed efforts to prove that Kerenidis and Prakash's quantum recommendation system algorithm [CITATION_1] achieves an exponential speedup over any classical algorithm. Such a result would be interesting because Kerenidis and Prakash's algorithm is a quantum machine learning (QML) algorithm.",
